These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
6 different games are played: monopoly, domino, poker, canasta, whist, billiard
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, indian, mexican, russian, spanish
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing domino##1
4. the russian is between the person playing billiard and the american##2
5. the mexican is between the russian and the argentine##2
6. the american is the person playing canasta##1
7. the person playing whist is on the left of the american##1
8. the spanish is on the left of the person playing domino##1
9. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Game           | monopoly | domino | billiard | whist | canasta    | poker  |
| Nationality   | spanish | argentine   | mexican       | russian        | american | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: october, january, february, september, december, may
6 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig, horse, lizard, snake
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in october##2
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Birthday   | january | may | december | september | february | october  |
| Pet           | snake | lizard  | frog | goat    | horse  | guinea-pig |

