.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, tennis, parkour, weightlifting, snowboarding, golf
The people use 6 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, taxi, tram, van
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person driving the helicopter##2
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | golf      | snowboarding | weightlifting | parkour      |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | van  | helicopter | taxi   | tram       | quad-bike |

