.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
There are 6 different nationalities: british, brazilian, dutch, australian, nigerian, italian
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, roller, scooter, taxi, trike
1. the person driving the roller is the australian##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the dutch##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the brazilian##1
5. the british is the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the bike and the italian##2
7. the brazilian is on the left of the italian##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Nationality        | brazilian    | italian | dutch | british | nigerian | australian   |
| Transport   | scooter | taxi        | quad-bike  | bike     | trike  | roller |

