.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, tea, juice, mirinda, fanta
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, cycling, golf, ice-hockey, soccer
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking mirinda##2
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Beverage   | 7up   | juice    | fanta | tea | milk | mirinda   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | badminton | cycling | soccer | golf  | biathlon |

