.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, pall-mall, ritmeester, siglo, baccarat, vegafina
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, reading, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the vegafina-smoker##1
8. the ritmeester-smoker is between the siglo-smoker and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
9. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Cigar    | bolivar | vegafina | baccarat  | siglo      | ritmeester | pall-mall  |
| Hobby   | card-games  | dancing    | reading | board-games | traveling | woodworking |

