4. the fonseca-smoker is the person driving the van##1
5. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the tram##2
7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
8. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
9. the person driving the boat is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Cigar       | baccarat | fonseca | aristoff | old-henry | cain | bluemaster |
| Transport   | quad-bike | van    | tram  | bike    | roller    | boat    |

