.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  designer, journalist, mechanic, musician, social-worker, teacher
There are 6 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, lemonade, water, iced-tea, cola
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking soy-milk##2
4. the musician is the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the mechanic is between the journalist and the social-worker##2
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the social-worker is on the right of the teacher##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the teacher##1
9. the mechanic is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Job           | musician | teacher | social-worker | mechanic | journalist | designer |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water   | sprite         | soy-milk    | cola     | iced-tea     |

