.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
City: marseilles, berlin, boston, hannover, prague, san-francisco
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, sailing, skateboarding, skiing, soccer, surfing
 1. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
10. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| City   | marseilles   | prague  | berlin | hannover | san-francisco | boston     |
| Sport   | sailing | biathlon | surfing    | soccer | skiing | skateboarding |

