.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-10::.
There 6 different types of food: banana, carrot, cucumber, pomegranate, artichoke, potato
6 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, goldfish, pony, rabbit, snake
1. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
2. the owner of the ferret is the person eating banana##1
3. the person eating artichoke is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person eating banana is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the person eating banana is between the person eating pomegranate and the person eating carrot##2
6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person eating banana##1
7. the person eating potato is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
8. the person eating potato is between the person eating pomegranate and the owner of the bird##2
9. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
| Food   | cucumber | potato | pomegranate   | banana | carrot | artichoke |
| Pet           | bird  | pony   | goldfish | ferret | snake       | rabbit |

