.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
6 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, frog, hedgehog, rabbit, snake
The people have 6 different hobbies: dancing, skydiving, card-games, traveling, hiking, magic-tricks
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the owner of the frog##2
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 9. the owner of the cat is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the owner of the chinchilla##2
10. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | snake   | rabbit | frog       | hedgehog | cat    | chinchilla |
| Hobby   | skydiving | hiking  | card-games | dancing      | traveling | magic-tricks        |

