.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, skateboard, motorbike, van, trike, scooter
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, family, musical, scientific, sports, time-travel
 1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching scientific movies##1
 4. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the van and the person watching time-travel movies##2
 5. the person watching musical movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person driving the trike##2
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is the person driving the car##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Transport           | skateboard      | van | motorbike | car   | scooter  | trike |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | comedy  | family             | time-travel | musical | sports       |

