.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
There 6 different types of food: avocado, banana, mango, onion, peas, zucchini
House: cape-cod, colonial, wooden, victorian, cottage, art-deco
 1. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 2. the art-deco house is between the cottage house and the person eating banana##2
 3. the cottage house is between the person eating zucchini and the cape-cod house##2
 4. the wooden house is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 5. the person eating zucchini is between the wooden house and the person eating mango##2
 6. the person eating onion is the colonial house##1
 7. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 8. the victorian house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 9. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
10. the person eating onion is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Food   | onion     | avocado | peas   | mango     | zucchini       | banana       |
| House    | colonial | victorian   | cape-cod | cottage | art-deco | wooden |

