 4. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of r&b is the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the fan of metal is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the fan of pop is the fan of pop##1
 8. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
10. the person driving the tram is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | trance | r&b    | metal     | disco      | pop    | classical |
| Transport   | ship | motorbike | quad-bike | tram | taxi | jet-ski  |

